@startuml
|User|
start
: (1) Click on Update button;
|System|
: (2) Display form to Update Employee;
|User|
repeat: (3) Fill needed information;
: (4) Click on Confirm button;
|System|
: Validate Updated Data;
backward: (5) Show error message;
repeat while (is Data valid?) is (no) not (yes)
: (6) Update Employee;
stop
@enduml
